    </article>

    <article class="timeline-item">
    <div class="experience-logo">
        <img src="/images/logos/purdue.png" alt="Purdue logo" />
      </div>
      <div class="experience-content">
      <h2>Graduate Teaching Assistant</h2>
      <p class="meta">Purdue ECE</p>
      <p>
        Led circuits lab sections, supported students during lab work, graded
        technical submissions, and communicated course logistics.
      </p>
      </div>
    </article>
  </section>
